gedoor.com.au";}}s:9:"sentences";a:66:{i:0;s:137:"My garage door has been working faultlessly for 5 years when all of a sudden it has decided that it wont close again after fully opening.";i:1;s:250:"Ive opened the unit and can confirm that when I activate the door motor unit using a remote that a relay can be heard clicking and I measured 24VDC for a moment on the circuit board output wires to the motor after which the voltage dropped off again.";i:2;s:105:"If the garage door opens correctly but fails to close completely there may be one of three common causes.";i:3;s:42:"The close-limit switch may need adjusting.";i:4;s:131:"Your garage door has set-limit switches that instruct the motor when to stop runningboth when it is opening and when it is closing.";i:5;s:42:"With this tool in hand follow these steps.";i:6;s:62:"Check the motor housing mounted to the ceiling of your garage.";i:7;s:56:"You should find two plastic screw heads or knobs on the.";i:8;s:88:"Start by rotating the down limit screw or knob one complete turn in the minus direction.";i:9;s:40:"Test the garage door to see if it stays.";i:10;s:107:"Incorrectly set limit switches may prevent your garage door from closing completely or opening all the way.";i:11;s:72:"Close the garage door with the opener and watch it closely as it closes.";i:12;s:136:"If the garage door does not close completely or begins to close and then opens back up again the down limit switch needs to be adjusted.";i:13;s:159:"Welcome to the Support Centre which contains all the resources you need for your Merlin Garage Door opener such as spare parts books brochures and user guides.";i:14;s:171:"Register your warranty here to ensure that you receive reminders about servicing your garage door opener as well as for peace of mind should you need your opener repaired.";i:15;s:106:"You can operate the door from a remote control radio transmitter or from a push-button inside your garage.";i:16;s:134:"One touch of the remote control button or internal push button will activate the opener and the door will open or close automatically.";i:17;s:100:"The door may be stopped in any position during the opening cycle by simply depressing either button.";i:18;s:118:"The first step is to locate the emergency release and disengage it do it only if the garage door is completely closed.";i:19;s:59:"Detach the opener by pulling the emergency handle downward.";i:20;s:62:"The next step is to attempt to open your garage door manually.";i:21;s:79:"This will determine if the issue is connected to the door itself or the opener.";i:22;s:127:"Wall Button Switch - If you have a hard wired Wall Button Switch you will need to check it still opens closes your Garage Door.";i:23;s:115:"This will isolate if it is just a problem with your Garage Remote or if the problem is with your Garage Door Motor.";i:24;s:154:"Other Garage Door Remotes - If you have other Garage Remotes operating the same Garage Door you will need to check if it is just the one Remote or all of.";i:25;s:126:"The Merlin roller door openers can fit to the left or right hand side of your garage door depending upon space and preference.";i:26;s:30:"This video outlines step-by-s.";i:27;s:96:"To manually open most garage doors you simply pull a corded handle that is attached to the door.";i:28;s:88:"This disengages the electric drive from the door and you can manually open and close it.";i:29;s:64:"To reset it begin by pulling the cord in the opposite direction.";i:30;s:25:"It should click in place.";i:31;s:65:"Once this happens you can open and close the door electronically.";i:32;s:107:"If your garage door opener no longer has power the Wi-Fi hub will send a command to the garage door opener.";i:33;s:146:"If there is an issue with the safety sensors and the door is unable to close normally this will also cause an issue closing the door from the app.";i:34;s:60:"Test the garage door opener from the remote or door control.";i:35;s:56:"If its not working troubleshoot your garage door opener.";i:36;s:27:"Try The Door Control Panel.";i:37;s:80:"If your door control has multiple functions check the Light button on the panel.";i:38;s:66:"Your door control panel is usually on the wall inside your garage.";i:39;s:94:"Sometimes the Light switch button is accidentally activated which causes the light to stay on.";i:40;s:119:"I can open or close the garage door away from home and the safety beam makes sure there is no obstacles before closing.";i:41;s:65:"The only slight inconvenience is that the LED light is a bit dim.";i:42;s:84:"Overall its a pleasure experience to use Merlin and I would definitely recommend it.";i:43;s:34:"Garage Door Opener Is Not Working.";i:44;s:100:"If your garage door opener no longer has power the myQ app will not activate the garage door opener.";i:45;s:171:"If there is an issue with the garage door opener preventing normal operation such as stripped gears or a bad logic board these will need to be resolved to use the myQ app.";i:46;s:97:"Discovered the problem recently whenever I close my garage door it opens automatically by itself.";i:47;s:94:"Rang service centre and adjusted down limit didnt work at all suggested maybe a motor problem.";i:48;s:170:"Also whenever after it opens automatically i can heard the motor noise from the opener itself for around 10 seconds then the built in light flashes for another 5 seconds.";i:49;s:177:"Although garage doors manufactured after the early 1990s in particular all have some type of safety door features they do not necessarily include the most up to date technology.";i:50;s:99:"Merlin garage door openers by The Chamberlain Group include a high standard of safety features but.";i:51;s:52:"Automatic garage door opener that is not responding.";i:52;s:66:"Automatic garage door opener remote is a very handy little device.";i:53;s:129:"Thanks to it you can enter or exit your garage at only one press of the button without having to lift up the heavy door yourself.";i:54;s:89:"The remote sends an infrared or IR signal to a receiver that pushes the switch making an.";i:55;s:65:"Check that the door opens from the openclose button on the motor.";i:56;s:70:"If lights are evident on the motor then check you batteries on remote.";i:57;s:46:"Further issues will require a door technician.";i:58;s:71:"Door opener does not operate with either the remote or the wall switch.";i:59;s:94:"Check that there is power to the motor by plugging in another appliance into the power source.";i:60;s:52:"Suitable for steel and timber spring balanced doors.";i:61;s:31:"Door Opening and Closing Times.";i:62;s:25:"Based on a 24m high door.";i:63;s:106:"With myQ you can close from anywhere open for anyone and get alerts when your garage door opens or closes.";i:64;s:29:"MERLIN POWERING GARAGE DOORS.";i:65;s:153:"From door openers to automated extras remotes keypads and even invisible light beams weve got every product you need to keep your garage safe and secure.";}}